# Product Requirements Document (PRD)
## LangChain Dashboard - AI Integration Showcase

**Version:** 1.1  
**Last Updated:** November 11, 2025  
**Project Type:** Static Web Application (GitHub Pages Compatible)  
**Status:** Production Ready

---

## 1. Executive Summary

The **LangChain Dashboard** is a comprehensive demonstration application showcasing three distinct AI integration patterns using LangChain.js and OpenAI's GPT-4.1-mini model. Built as a static single-page application, it demonstrates conversational AI with memory, template-driven prompt engineering, and direct LLM queriesâ€”all within a modern, accessible interface featuring pastel green and dark green theming.

### Key Value Propositions

- **Educational Tool**: Demonstrates three fundamental AI integration patterns for developers learning LangChain
- **Client-Side Architecture**: Fully static deployment compatible with GitHub Pages, Netlify, or Vercel
- **Modern UX**: Responsive design with dark/light theme support, scrollable result cards, and accessible UI components
- **Recipe Management**: Built-in local storage system for saving and managing AI-generated recipes
- **Example-Driven Learning**: Interactive "Try these examples" buttons for quick exploration of AI capabilities
- **Overflow Protection**: Smart text wrapping and scrolling to handle lengthy AI responses gracefully

